g.text: Accelerate customer adoption of Azure We are a cross-functional team focused on rapid execution. If you have a funded, strategic, or compete opportunity with customer buy-in and authorization to deploy, we can help you quicky move from ideation to deployment.

Support organization-wide scalabilityEach engagement includes a retrospective resulting in learnings that are strategically turned into reusable assets. This includes presentations, demonstrations, reference architectures, and best practices for our teammates, partners, and customers.
